To find the $\goldE{\text{total}}$ number of capitals Ari can name, we start with the number of capitals $\blueE{\text{Rani}}$ can name, and add how many $\maroonD{\text{fewer}}$ names she can name than Ari.

![](web+graphie://cdn.kastatic.org/ka-perseus-graphie/b7c4efcbdc13153ed30ec9233639c8cb41f02836)

$\begin{align}
\blueE{\text{Rani}} + \maroonD{21}  &= \goldE{\text{Ari}} \\\\
\blueE{48} + \maroonD{21} &= \goldE{\Box}
\end{align}$
